  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to monitor the performance and of the Silent Hip™ in the
      treatment of patients with hip joint disease requiring a total hip replacement. Patients who
      enter the study will be evaluated at regular intervals following hip surgery using patient,
      clinical and x-ray assessments.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
